    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight alongside an AI that learns your unique <strong>playstyle.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an adventure with a mysterious AI that grows stronger the more you teach it. <br><i>BlockWorld Ai</i> is an <strong>AI-training puzzle RPG</strong> where you battle alongside “Hoshihabito-kun,” an AI that learns how you solve puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To save the Friends who have turned hostile, your wisdom becomes your greatest weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The AI Learns from Your Moves</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your decisions. <br>Your chain reactions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The AI <strong>remembers them and evolves.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The AI you raise will operate the puzzle board during boss battles.<br>Using the strategies it has learned, it fights on its own.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Strategic Puzzle Where Numbers Decide the Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the numbers written on the blocks to subtract from the “target number” and bring it down to zero. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the target number reaches zero, a chain reaction is triggered. <br>Match three of the same blocks to attack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple to play, yet deeply strategic.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss Battles with the AI You Raised</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Standing before the boss is the AI you nurtured. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the strategies it has learned, it moves the board and fights on its own. <br>Its actions <strong>reflect your playstyle</strong>—fighting with the same judgment you taught it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support it with skills and fight together for victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Activate Skills with Diagonal Matches</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Align blocks diagonally through the center to activate the Friends’ skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up SP to unleash powerful special moves. <br>Turn the tide of battle in an instant!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Treasure Collection &amp; Enhancement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the cubes you collect to obtain treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The combination of growth and strategy unlocks new possibilities for your AI.</p>",
